Sequlize cli library

## Introduce

install npm install --save sequelize-cli

init node_modules/.bin/sequelize init

Mac  sequelize:	alias sequelize='node_modules/.bin/sequelize'

 config/config.json  databaseschema username password 

## Migration

create migration by model 

	node_modules/.bin/sequelize model:generate --name User

create migration

	node_modules/.bin/sequelize migration:create --name add-wechatid-in-user

## Seed

demo  dat

 demo-user  seed 

	node_modules/.bin/sequelize seed:generate --name demo-user

seeder 

	'use strict';
	module.exports = {
	  up: (queryInterface, Sequelize) => {
	    return queryInterface.bulkInsert('Users', [{
	        firstName: 'John',
	        lastName: 'Doe',
	        email: 'demo@demo.com'
	      }], {});
	  },

	  down: (queryInterface, Sequelize) => {
	    return queryInterface.bulkDelete('Users', null, {});
	  }
	};


Reference 

[Sequelize ](http://docs.sequelizejs.com/manual/tutorial/migrations.html)

